01:01.161 --> 01:05.330
It was that fateful day
that I sent him to bring peace.

01:05.331 --> 01:07.633
That was one of the worst days
in South Bronx history.

01:07.635 --> 01:10.803
The word on the street was that
he was trying to make peace,

01:10.805 --> 01:12.638
and he was murdered
trying to make peace.

01:12.640 --> 01:14.640
Basically after that,
the South Bronx,

01:14.642 --> 01:16.308
fort Apache was out of control.

01:16.310 --> 01:18.110
They were running
through the streets.

01:18.112 --> 01:20.232
They were burning everything.
I mean, pandemonium hit.

01:27.854 --> 01:29.488
I put out a bulletin,

01:29.490 --> 01:32.558
and I started calling
all the ghetto brothers.

01:32.560 --> 01:34.660
Charlie wanted
to get the ghetto brothers

01:34.662 --> 01:37.229
to mobilize
for the biggest bloodbath

01:37.231 --> 01:38.797
in the history of New York.

01:38.799 --> 01:40.499
We lost a member.

01:40.501 --> 01:42.367
They viciously murdered him
out there in the street.

01:42.369 --> 01:43.869
Now It's an eye for an eye.

01:43.871 --> 01:48.107
The Bronx was gonna be bathed in
blood.

01:55.248 --> 01:58.217
How rumors spread,
how news spread.

01:58.219 --> 02:01.420
There was not a gang
in the whole of New York

02:01.422 --> 02:02.788
that was not aware
what's happening.

02:02.790 --> 02:05.190
And it was like
the movie "the warriors"

